EXTRACTED VALUE: It's notable to mention that this is the first game that allows for 16-player Co-op and playing through the Mission mode setting against enemy A.I.
Project Gotham is still a series plugging away in a league of its own, but this time in every sense. Absolutely astounding.
This isn't a game about time, it's about memories, and how they can be repeated and eventually rewritten.
A fantastic effort, and worth the cash to own this one outright.
As a co-op experience and as a tactical shooter, Rainbow Six Vegas sets a new benchmark for the gaming industry.
An unparalleled, one-of-a-kind experience that represents the very best that gaming has to offer.
